# Phase Start Workflow (Mandatory)

Before starting implementation for any phase, complete this sequence in order:

1. Review all documents related to the target phase.
2. Review the code from completed phases to understand existing patterns and dependencies.
3. Switch to plan mode and produce an implementation plan for the phase.
4. Start implementation only after steps 1-3 are complete.

Do not skip or reorder these steps unless the user explicitly asks to override this workflow.
